  "name": "RPlog_Into_The_Nexu_Den",
  "title": "A Pirate's Night Out on Nar Shaddaa",
  "summary": "The Imperial pilot Liza Molokai, on a few days' leave, follows the pirate Juran into the rowdy Beggar's Cove Cantina on Nar Shaddaa, nervous and out of her element. Juran plies the sheltered Sarian with his potent caff-and-lum liquor and a sniff of recreational spice before dressing up to show her the city. He drags her through the throbbing Concourse to the Pleasure Palace, where rather than anything untoward he treats her to a full bathhouse pampering of massages, oils, and doting attendants, leaving her thoroughly relaxed. Over a meal at the Meltdown Cafe, Liza offers to help Juran with the dire medical situation she glimpsed on a datapad, an offer he gruffly waves off as getting what he deserves, and the two trade banter about killing, morality, and pirate callsigns as Juran teasingly threatens to nickname her 'Squeak.' As the night wears on Liza, a lightweight, drinks far too much Corellian Twister and gradually slides into slurring drunkenness, until Juran finally leads the staggering pilot off to sleep it off.",
